  "text": "Nucleotide sequences of the desaturases were aligned by using the program ClustalX 2.0.10 (Thompson et al., 1994) and manual adjustment. The phylogenetic tree was generated using the alignment output based on the Minimum evolution method [CITATION_1] , as implemented in the Mega 4.1 [CITATION_2] . The complete deletion option and the Jukes and Cantor metric were used, and confidence of the tree branches was checked by bootstrap generated from 1000 replicates.",
